<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 qióng cāng shuō zhǔ bì kuài lái, dà de shuō zhǔ bì kuài lái,
 gāo shān shuō zhǔ bì kuài lái, hǎi yáng shuō zhǔ bì kuài lái,
 shì jiè yǐ xiǎn chū yù zhào, wàn wù shuō zhǔ bì kuài lái,
 nà rì dà ér kě wèi, chén shuì de rén kuài sū xǐng,
 yù bèi ba! diǎn liàng dēng, zhǔ shuō tā bì kuài lái,
 shuì xǐng ba shù shàng dài zi, zhǔ shuō tā bù zài děng dài.</lyrics>
<title>zhǔ bì kuài lái 迦南157</title>
<hymn_number>157</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
</song>